item.title: Godwars dungeon
item.dc:creator: @danimaster danimaster
item.description:
@danimaster wrote:

[quote=“pure kirk, post:5, topic:276786”]dude u want a portal right if u do go to newobject
copy one of the codes there
e.g.
makeGlobalObject(3093, 3503, 2156, 1, 10);
3093, 3503 means x and y coords to find theese out on ur server go to the place where u wanna spawn the portal and press ::mypos
the 2156 means the object u wish to spawn
ignore the 1 10 there for views…
kk now were done with tht
go to ur client.java once again hit ctrl +f
and…
type this in
King Black Dragon lair it should take u to this
if(objectID == 2468){
toX = 3016;
toY = 3849;
sM(“You teleport to the King Black Dragon lair!”);
}
the x and y coords i made up
kk under that add

if(objectID == ####){
triggerTele2(****, ****, 0);
sM(“Message it sends!!!”);
}
kk in the #### area switch that to object id
**** is the x and y coords
the reason i used trigger tele 2 is because is now if some1 is tbed they wont be able to use it.
if u dont have a message jus delete sm area
hope it helps[/quote]
thnx dude problem solved!
